 -H "W-Token: <%=@wiw_token%>"
```
```php
<?php
$wiw = new Wheniwork("<%=@wiw_token%>");
$result = $wiw->delete("shifts/1337");
?>
```

> Example Response

```json
{
  "success": true
}
```

### HTTP Request
`DELETE <%=@api_prefix%>/2/shifts/{id}`

### Parameters

Key | Description
--- | -----------
